name: Zillow Home Value Index (Cities): Median Sale Price per Sq. Ft. - Gig Harbor, WA
description: The Zillow Home Value Index is Zillow's estimate of the median market value of median sale price per sq. ft. within the city of Gig Harbor, WA. This data is calculated by Zillow Real Estate Research (www.zillow.com/research) using their database of 110 million homes.
